Christopher Fulford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christopher_Fulford 0 Christopher Fulford (born 1955, London) is a British actor who is best known for his supporting roles in many British TV shows, one of the earliest being punk Alex in the short lived sitcom Sorry, I'm A Stranger Here Myself (1981).
